{
  "texts": [
    "We first analyze the end-to-end performance of Jellyfish under a synthetic network trace.",
    "Following AWStream (Zhang et al. 2018a), we periodically set each client's 1 3",
    "Real-Time Systems (2024) 60:239-290 bandwidth to a value from the ordered set {20, 15, 10, 7.5}Mbps and keep each value for 20 seconds.",
    "We test with {1, 2, 4, 8} concurrent clients and draw their SLOs from the set of {75, 100, 150} milliseconds (ms) and request rates from the set of {15, 25} FPS.",
    "The smallest DNN in the DNN zoo has P99 latency of 23ms for batch size 1."
  ]
}